## 🔍 Verify Data Intervals

### Check timestamp spacing:
```powershell
sqlcmd -S "(localdb)\mssqllocaldb" -d "TelemetryDb" -Q "SELECT TOP 5 d.DeviceId, t.Timestamp, t.Value FROM Telemetries t INNER JOIN Devices d ON t.DeviceId = d.Id WHERE d.DeviceId = 'device-001' ORDER BY t.Timestamp ASC"
```

### Check interval statistics:
```powershell
sqlcmd -S "(localdb)\mssqllocaldb" -d "TelemetryDb" -Q "SELECT COUNT(*) as TotalRecords FROM Telemetries"
```

