## ✨ Benefits of 2-Minute Intervals

✅ **Realistic IoT pattern** - Real sensors typically don't send data every second  
✅ **Better visualization** - Charts are easier to read with spaced-out data points  
✅ **Reduced database load** - Less frequent writes  
✅ **Historical trends** - Easier to see patterns over time  
✅ **Production-like** - Mimics real-world IoT deployments  

